zosin: a new alpha adrenoceptor blocking drug." J Clin Pharmacol 32 (1992): 520-3[6] Kuokkanen K, Mattila MJ "Demonstration of an additive antihypertensive effect of prazosin and polythiazide in out-patient." Curr Ther Res Clin Exp 17 (1975): 431-6[7] "Product Information. Orlaam (levomethadyl acetate)" Roxanne Laboratories Inc, Columbus, OH.', 'Acamprosate, Naltrexone, Varenicline, Disulfiram, Nalmefene, Nicotine', 'Hydroflumethiazide, Trichlormethiazide, Methyclothiazide, Tinidazole, Ascorbic acid, Hydroflumethiazide, Simeprevir, Rosuvastatin, Sulfadiazine, Lactic acid, Clindamycin, More', 1767369485);
