y." Clin Pharmacol Ther 67 (2000): 451-7[3] Patel S, Robinson R, Burk M "Hypertensive crisis associated with St. John''s Wort." Am J Med 112 (2002): 507-8', 'Citalopram, Sertraline, Maprotiline, Fluoxetine, Milnacipran, Vortioxetine, Levomilnacipran, Doxepin, Duloxetine, Isocarboxazid, Amoxapine, More', NULL, 1767369485);
